		  <td class="forum_boardrow1" style="border-width: 0px 1px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="message29373331">I liked the colorful art style, but contrary to those above me, I actually liked that fact that there was a plot. I think I would've gotten bored if it was just silliness for the entire anime. And I didn't really like the music... (but hey, de gustibus non est disputandum). And yeah, the idea of using social media to help the community was interesting, especially since the anime made social media personas tangible.</div><div class="postActions"></div><div class="sig"><!--link--><a href="http://myanimelist.net/animelist/einonymous&amp;sclick=1"><img class="userimg" data-src="http://myanimelist.net/signature/einonymous.png" /></a> </div></td>
